description:
Let’s go diving! Deep within the ocean lurk sharks, electric eels, and harmful squid. Can you reach the surface without touching the squid? It’s your job to bring surface safely! Bounce on rocky ledges and use Starfish as a boost. Collect golden coins to unlock new diving characters.

EXCITING FUN AND ITS FREE TO DOWNLOAD!!!

Challenge Your Friends for Highest Score!
